Sentencas: BaxSr1-xCo0.6Fe0.4O3-delta (0.2 <= x <= 0.8) synthesized by conventional solid state reaction method forms single phase solid solutions.
Titulo: Investigation on Structure and Electrical Property of Perovskite Type BaxSr1-xCo0.6Fe0.4O3-δ (x=0.2-0.8) Oxides

Sentencas: The orthorhombic strontium cobaltite structure of host changes from orthorhombic to cubic with the increase in Ba mole fraction to x = 0.3, and again to orthorhombic for x = 0.4.
Titulo: Investigation on Structure and Electrical Property of Perovskite Type BaxSr1-xCo0.6Fe0.4O3-δ (x=0.2-0.8) Oxides

Sentencas: For x >= 0.5, hexagonal barium cobaltite structure is obtained.
Titulo: Investigation on Structure and Electrical Property of Perovskite Type BaxSr1-xCo0.6Fe0.4O3-δ (x=0.2-0.8) Oxides

Sentencas: All the samples with different compositions comprise of small particles and big agglomerates.
Titulo: Investigation on Structure and Electrical Property of Perovskite Type BaxSr1-xCo0.6Fe0.4O3-δ (x=0.2-0.8) Oxides

Sentencas: The maximum electronic conductivity sigma = 127.95 S cm(-1) at 720 degrees C is found in case of Ba0.5Sr0.5Co0.6Fe0.4O3-delta
Titulo: Investigation on Structure and Electrical Property of Perovskite Type BaxSr1-xCo0.6Fe0.4O3-δ (x=0.2-0.8) Oxides
